    <item>
      <title>波兰央行行长警告通胀复苏，降息预期逐渐减弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/polish-rate-cut-bets-fade-as-governor-warns-of-inflation-revival</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在央行行长 Adam Glapinski 警告称通胀可能在 2024 年下半年再次螺旋式上升后，交易员减少了对波兰货币宽松规模的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/polish-rate-cut-bets-fade-as-governor-warns-of-inflation-revival</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 12:34:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>船只刊登中国链接广告以避免胡塞武装在红海发动袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/ships-advertise-chinese-links-to-avoid-houthi-attack-in-red-sea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[至少有五艘穿越红海的船只正在使用信号表明它们与中国有联系——为避免红海胡塞武装分子袭击而采取的最新不寻常措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/ships-advertise-chinese-links-to-avoid-houthi-attack-in-red-sea</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 12:29:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2023 年巴西通胀率高于预测但在目标范围内</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/brazil-s-annual-inflation-slows-within-target-range-by-december</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西去年的年度通胀虽然仍处于央行的承受范围内，但降幅低于预期，凸显了宽松货币政策面临的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/brazil-s-annual-inflation-slows-within-target-range-by-december</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 12:05:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯2023年石​​油和天然气收入受制裁、原油价格下跌影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/russian-government-s-2023-oil-and-gas-revenue-curbed-by-sanctions-cheaper-crude</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年，俄罗斯预算赤字扩大幅度超出预期，原因是石油和天然气收入下降了近四分之一，而且克里姆林宫在乌克兰战争期间增加了支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/russian-government-s-2023-oil-and-gas-revenue-curbed-by-sanctions-cheaper-crude</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 11:56:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国邮局丑闻：受害者仍在争取赔偿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-11/uk-post-office-scandal-victims-still-fighting-for-damages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 周三宣布了一项法律，撤销对约 980 名因盗窃和虚假会计罪被错误定罪的英国邮局工作人员的定罪，并加快赔偿速度。 Sabah Meddings 和 Bloomberg Opinion 专栏作家 Adrian Wooldridge 在 Bloomberg Television 上提供了详细信息。伍德里奇的观点仅代表他自己。 （更正了图形和描述中伍德里奇名字的拼写。）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-11/uk-post-office-scandal-victims-still-fighting-for-damages</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 11:06:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
