      <title>伦敦市长称脱欧使英国经济损失1400亿英镑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/brexit-erased-140-billion-from-uk-economy-london-mayor-to-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦市长萨迪克·汗周四将英国经济损失1400亿英镑（1780亿美元）归咎于英国脱欧，呼吁政府“紧急”重建与欧盟的关系以阻止经济衰退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/brexit-erased-140-billion-from-uk-economy-london-mayor-to-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 10:50:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
